        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_FacilitySelect",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve a paginated list of facilities from the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Billing.Facility",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table based on optional search criteria. It supports sorting by various columns and allows for flexible pagination. The procedure also calculates the total number of records that match the search criteria, which is useful for pagination purposes."
        }
      ]
    },
