                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The use of "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "CASE",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " statements for sorting can be inefficient, especially if the table is large, as it may prevent the use of indexes."
